{"word":"H2686 - חָצַץ - châtsats - khaw-tsats' - Archer","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">חָצַץ</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>châtsats"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>khaw-tsats'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Archer"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - வில்வீரர், குறுக்கப்படு, சேர்"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"1) to divide"},{"paragraph":"a) (Qal) to divide"},{"paragraph":"b) (Piel) to divide"},{"paragraph":"c) (Pual) to be cut off, to be finished"},{"paragraph":"2) to shoot arrows; (Piel) an archer (participle)"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> A primitive root (compare <a href=\"#/H2673 - חָצָה - châtsâh - khaw-tsaw'/2673\">H2673</a>); properly to <i>chop</i> into, pierce or sever; hence to <i>curtail</i>, to <i>distribute</i> (into ranks); as denominative from <a href=\"#/H2671 - חֵץ - chêts - khayts/2671\">H2671</a>; to <i>shoot</i> an arrow: - archer, X bands, cut off in the midst."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H2671 - חֵץ - chêts - khayts/2671\">H2671</a>, <a href=\"#/H2686 - חָצַץ - châtsats - khaw-tsats'/2686\">H2686</a>, <a href=\"#/H2687 - חָצָץ - châtsâts - khaw-tsawts'/2687\">H2687</a>, <a href=\"#/H2688 - חַצְצֹון תָּמָר - Chatsᵉtsôwn Tâmâr - khats-ets-one' taw-mawr'/2688\">H2688</a>"}]}